DelegatingXmlDictionaryReader Class

Definition

A class that wraps a specified reader and delegates all XmlDictionaryReader calls to the wrapped reader.

In this Article

public class DelegatingXmlDictionaryReader : System.Xml.XmlDictionaryReader

Remarks

The reader that is wrapped can be accessed through the InnerReader property. Call the InitializeInnerReader method to set the wrapped reader and initialize the property.
